<div class="row banner-image">
  <img src="<%= image_url('walk-wide.jpg') %>" class='img-fluid' style='width:100% z-index: -1;'>
  <h1 class='display-1 text-center w hidden-sm-down' style="position: absolute; bottom:25%; width: 100%; font-family: 'Changa One', cursive; z-index:100;">#NFSTRONG</h1>
  <h4 class='display-2 text-center w hidden-sm-down' style="position: absolute; bottom:15%; width: 100%; font-family: 'Just Another Hand', cursive;">Striding toward a future without NF</h4>
  <div class='col-md-3 hidden-sm-down offset-3 text-center' style="position: absolute; bottom:5%; width: 100%;">
    <%= link_to "Register", register_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-block' %>
  </div>
  <div class='col-md-3 hidden-sm-down offset-6 text-center' style="position: absolute; bottom:5%; width: 100%;">
    <%= link_to "Contribute", contribution_select_path, class: 'btn btn-success btn-block' %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class='container mt-4'>
  <div class='row mt-5'>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <h3>About Our Events</h3>
      <p>Walks for Neurofibromatosis take place in communities nationwide.  
      These inspiring events create strong bonds that build a supportive NF community.  
      The goal of these strong communities is to rally together and become one great voice in 
      finding affective treatments and an eventual cure for NF.  The walks are a great way to 
      involve family and friends, meet others who are affected by NF, while raising awareness 
      of this disorder and to create funding for NF research. Take your first step towards a cure 
      by finding, registering, and then fundraising for a walk near you!</p>
      
      <br>
      <h3>Event Activites</h3>
      <p>Join us at #NFStrong events for fun, food, face painting, a raffle with fabulous prizes, NF tattoos, 
      NF Champion medals, top fundraising certificates, and new friends.</p>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
        <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/018O0TMy8fc?rel=0&showinfo=0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
      <h3 class='text-center mt-4' style="font-family: 'Boogaloo', cursive;">Share With Friends</h3>
    <ul class='nav justify-content-center pr-1 mt-2'>
      <li class='nav-item'><a class='nav-link' href='https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=<%= request.original_url %>' target="_blank"><i class='fa fa-facebook-square fa-3x social-icon' style='color:#3b5998;'></i></a></li>
